### 加载推荐视频
GET {{host}}/video/loadRecommendVideo
Content-Type: application/json

### 加载视频列表 - 全部视频 (不按分类)
POST {{host}}/video/loadVideo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageNo": 1
}

### 加载视频列表 - 按父分类过滤
POST {{host}}/video/loadVideo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pCategoryId": 1,
  "pageNo": 1
}

### 加载视频列表 - 按子分类过滤
POST {{host}}/video/loadVideo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pCategoryId": 1,
  "categoryId": 101,
  "pageNo": 1
}

### 加载视频分片列表
POST {{host}}/video/loadVideoPList
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "1001"
}

### 获取视频详情
POST {{host}}/video/getVideoInfo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "1001"
}

### 获取推荐视频(基于关键词)
POST {{host}}/video/getVideoRecommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "Kotlin",
  "videoId": "1001"
}

### 搜索视频
POST {{host}}/video/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "Spring",
  "pageNo": 1
}

### 搜索视频 - 带排序类型
POST {{host}}/video/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "Kotlin",
  "orderType": 1,
  "pageNo": 1
}

### 获取热门搜索关键词
GET {{host}}/video/getSearchKeywordTop
Content-Type: application/json

### 加载热门视频列表
POST {{host}}/video/loadHotVideoList
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageNo": 1
}

### 加载热门视频列表 - 第2页
POST {{host}}/video/loadHotVideoList
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageNo": 2
}
